WEBVTT

00:09:00.888 --> 00:09:02.441
Because, you know --

00:09:02.465 --> 00:09:04.990
(Applause)

00:09:08.546 --> 00:09:11.335
Because you know that migration,

00:09:11.359 --> 00:09:12.818
just like mothering,

00:09:12.842 --> 00:09:14.557
is an act of hope.

00:09:15.586 --> 00:09:18.496
Now, not every mother
thinks like a mother.

00:09:18.520 --> 00:09:22.095
When presented with a choice,
some of us have made the wrong one,

00:09:22.119 --> 00:09:25.507
hiding behind weapons
or barbed wire or privilege

00:09:25.531 --> 00:09:27.714
to deny the rest of the world,

00:09:27.738 --> 00:09:33.110
thinking they can see their way to safety
in some kind of armed lifeboat